---
title: One-Pot Beef and Black Bean Chili with Spicy Crema and Monterey Jack Cheese
description: A good chili has well-seasoned beef, creamy beans, and tender vegetables. A great chili, however, has all that and comes together in one pot in under an hour. This chili is one of the greats. And once you take a bite, we can guarantee you’ll agree. Not to mention, these beefy bowls are adorned with some delicious fixings: tangy hot sauce crema and melty Monterey Jack. If you’ve got some on hand, why not crumble up some tortilla chips and sprinkle them on top for a crunch?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-beef-black-bean-chili-d2f5e646.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pot-beef-black-bean-chili-5d76b40292f8cd000f15374a-da8e83fd.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pot-beef-and-black-bean-chili-5d76b40292f8cd000f15374a
course: main course
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 780 kcal
